    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏交流群：614389592</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用卡牌驱动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如将角色卡放在场景卡上，角色将自动探索该位置。或者将角色卡和道具卡放在一起，组合成新的道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336580/extras/14c5a19a093138f4b5f8b73e8a87d482.avif?t=1771997754\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然了，角色不止一名，你会在游戏中遇见数十名可招募的角色，组成小队一起探索这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336580/extras/1cc9ad5fd3cedde0e007dafcbfe7eff7.avif?t=1771997754\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索总是伴随着危险，你会遇到各种各样的敌人，这时需要你把角色组成合适的build，用你的智慧巧妙的击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336580/extras/b221c705bc669f0071773e4b486c0a0a.avif?t=1771997754\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人或探索世界时会获得物品，你可以将物品组合成各种道具或料理以培养你的角色，以展开更深入的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336580/extras/96e66d3bbd1c7145eed1237eb7b0c111.avif?t=1771997754\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着冒险的深入，你会和各种人和事相遇，在这其中做出你的选择，找到你的归途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336580/extras/9f247c9484ce90baefdcb2cb4d366b06.avif?t=1771997754\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏在研发过程中结合了一定的AI技术支持，如您对此有特殊偏好或顾虑，还请酌情选择是否体验。感谢您的理解与支持。</p></li></ul>",
